---- MODULE CapabilityToken ----
\* Capability token lifecycle. Tokens are linear resources — granted once, checked N times, revoked exactly once.
\* Generated by tlaiser — https://github.com/hyperpolymath/tlaiser

EXTENDS Naturals, Sequences, TLC

\* State constants — each represents a distinct state
CONSTANTS Ungranted, Active, Revoked

\* Variables tracked by this specification
VARIABLES state, resource_kind

\* Type invariant: state is always one of the declared states
TypeInvariant == state \in {Ungranted, Active, Revoked}

\* Initial state predicate
Init ==
    /\ state = Ungranted
    /\ resource_kind = 0

\* Transition actions
\* Transition: Ungranted -> Active (cap_grant)
cap_grant ==
    /\ state = Ungranted
    /\ state' = Active
    /\ UNCHANGED resource_kind

\* Transition: Active -> Active (cap_check)
cap_check ==
    /\ state = Active
    /\ state' = Active
    /\ UNCHANGED resource_kind

\* Transition: Active -> Revoked (cap_revoke)
cap_revoke ==
    /\ state = Active
    /\ state' = Revoked
    /\ UNCHANGED resource_kind

\* Next-state relation: disjunction of all transitions
Next ==
    \/ cap_grant
    \/ cap_check
    \/ cap_revoke

\* All variables tuple (for stuttering)
vars == <<state, resource_kind>>

\* Complete specification
Spec == Init /\ [][Next]_vars

\* Fair specification (with weak fairness on Next)
FairSpec == Spec /\ WF_vars(Next)

\* ---- Temporal Properties ----
\* Property: GuardedWindowCannotClose (safety)
GuardedWindowCannotClose == []([][WindowGuard # Free => WindowLifecycle # Closed]_WindowLifecycle)

\* Property: RevokedTokenNeverChecked (safety)
RevokedTokenNeverChecked == []([][CapabilityToken = Revoked => UNCHANGED CapabilityToken]_CapabilityToken)

\* Property: WindowEventuallyRuns (liveness)
WindowEventuallyRuns == <>(<>(WindowLifecycle = Running))


====
